comments.value: #Sample Feature Definition Template ECOM-10243 & ECOM-10253 having 8 test cases

elements.name: Flow of SIM Free with any accessory

steps.name: I am an eComm user
I add 'sim free' device in my basket along with any accessory
I SHOULD be shown a 'Remove' CTA in front of the 'sim free device'
Remove the device from the basket, If I click on Remove

elements.name: Flow of SIM Free with Pay Monthly sim

steps.name: I am an eComm user
I add 'sim free' device in my basket along with Pay Monthly sim
I SHOULD be shown a 'Remove' CTA in front of the 'sim free device'
Remove the device from the basket, If I click on Remove

elements.name: Flow of SIM Free with PAYG sim and an accessory

steps.name: I am an eComm user
I add 'sim free' device in my basket along with PAYG sim and an accessory
I SHOULD be shown a 'Remove' CTA in front of the 'sim free device'
Remove the device as well as the PAYG Sim from the basket, If I click on 'Remove'

elements.name: Flow of SIM Free with PayM with accessory

steps.name: I am an eComm user
I add 'sim free' device in my basket along with PayM and an accessory
I SHOULD be shown a 'Remove' CTA in front of the 'sim free device'
Remove the device from the basket, If I click on Remove

elements.name: Flow of SIM Free with SIM Free Device

steps.name: I am an eComm user
My basket contains 'Sim free' device only
I SHOULD NOT be shown a 'Remove' CTA in front of the 'sim free device'

elements.name: Flow of SIM Free with PAYG Sim

steps.name: I am an eComm user
My basket contains 'Sim free' device with PAYG Sim
I SHOULD NOT be shown a 'Remove' CTA in front of the 'sim free device'

elements.name: Flow to validate the Basket Page

steps.name: I am an eComm user
I add Sim free device along with the Airtime plan"PayG"
Land on basket page
I SHOULD be able to see the Sim free Device and Airtime plan separately - please see the attached design

name: Validation of the Remove CTA feature
